Fatal accident at Bukit batok ave 5Dear readers I am leveraging on the power of social media to appeal for witnesses of a fatal traffic accident. The details are as below :Date : 28th July 2022Location : Bukit Batok Ave 5 towards Brickland Road Area ( beside Zu-Lin temple Heavy Vehicle carpark)Estimated time : Roughly between 7pm - 7.30pmScene : Black Bike (RSV4 Aprillia - FBJ5070M)& White Mini Bus (Fuso - PC7763E)This accident has claimed my nephew's life. He passed away on 28 July 2022.From what we know  he was riding on a straight road and the driver of the mini bus was making his turn (either to enter the heavy vehicle carpark or making a u-turn).We are humbly appealling for any eye witnesses who were driving/riding on the same road to step forward and share any video recordings of this accident to help with the investigations  and for our family to seek closure with our dreadful loss.Kindly do contact me at90662639(Manje) or87842720(Saiful).If there were any videos taken of the accident after it happened  we would appreciate it if they are not circulated in social media and text messaging platforms. Please do not speculate on this while it is under investigations.Thank you.
